      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "NAT",
      "stem": "At a point, $\\sigma_x = 80\\,\\text{MPa}$, $\\sigma_y = 0$ and $\\tau_{xy}=0$. The maximum shear stress is _____ MPa.",
      "answer": 40,
      "tolerance": 0.1,
      "solution": "**Concept.** $\\tau_{max}=\\dfrac{\\sigma_1-\\sigma_2}{2}$. Here $\\sigma_1=80,\\sigma_2=0$.\n\n**Working.**\n$$\\tau_{max}=\\dfrac{80-0}{2}=40.$$\n\n**Answer.** $40\\,\\text{MPa}$",
      "archetype": "A",
      "marks": 2
